---
title: Baked American Chicken Drumsticks with Fries & Creamy Corn Slaw
description: Sink your teeth into an oven-roasted chicken drumstick - we will look the other way if you use your hands. Serve up with a side of fries and an onion chutney to a touch of sweetness to this delicious dish.
